      • readFile

        private static YagoEntry[] readFile(java.lang.String filePath,
                                    java.lang.String searchTerm,
                                    int searchField,
                                    int max_find)
                             throws java.io.IOException
        reads yago files and collects entries that match searchTerm AND searchField
        Parameters:
        filePath - a yago file path
        searchTerm - a string to search for, override by "Dosen't Matter"
        searchField - a coded manner to make different comparisons, see cmp
        max_find - maximum number of entries to retrieve.
        Returns:
        an array of YagoEntry containing matches
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - Signals that an I/O exception of some sort has occurred.
